{"word":"H7951 - שָׁלָה - shâlâh - shaw-law' - Be happy","slug":"H7951","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be happy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05D5;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - sha&#x0302;la&#x0302;h  sha&#x0302;lav</b> - <i>shaw-law', shaw-lav'</i><p/>The second form being used in <a href='B:220 3:26'>Job 3:26</a>; a primitive root; to be <i>tranquil</i>, that is, <i>secure</i> or <i>successful</i>: - be happy, prosper, be in safety."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7952\">H7952</a>, <a href=\"#/H7956\">H7956</a>, <a href=\"#/H7959\">H7959</a>, <a href=\"#/H7961\">H7961</a>, <a href=\"#/H7962\">H7962</a>, <a href=\"#/H7987\">H7987</a>, <a href=\"#/H8024\">H8024</a>"}]}